Package slu.compiler

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ILexicalAnalyzer
    ILexicalAnalyzer is an interface that defines the public methods of the lexical analyzer
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayType
    ArrayType is a DataType subclass
    DataType
    DataType is the superclass of ArrayType, and PrimitiveType subclasses
    Identifier
    Identifier is a Token subclass
    IntegerNumber
    IntegerNumber is a Token subclass
    LexicalAnalyzer
    LexicalAnalyzer is a custom-made scanner to be used in CS3200 Programming Languages.
    Lexicon
    Lexicon is a Hashtable (String, String) containing the tokens of the language, defined as the key-value [lexeme, token-name] The file lexicon.txt defines the tokens and the lexemes of the language.
    PrimitiveType
    PrimitiveType is a DataType subclass
    RealNumber
    RealNumber is a Token subclass
    Token
    Token is the superclass of Identifier, IntegerNumber and RealNumber subclasses
